<pageContent>
    <id><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D060]]></id>
	<title><![CDATA[<Introtext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; color:#cc0033; margin:10px -5px 10px 5px; width:738px; padding:5px 0 5px 5px; background:#e8e8e8; border-bottom:1px solid #333; display:block;">Personal Value Message</Introtext>]]></title>
	<title2><![CDATA[Personal Value Message]]></title2>
	<instructions><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:11pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:bold; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">How will you summarize and conclude your meeting with Dr. Gomez?</welcomeText >]]></instructions>
	<choices>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[1]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>A</b>. “I will support you by leaving you the materials and information that you need.”  </welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="5">
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D060_A010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[2]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[YES]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>B</b>. “Dr. Gomez, we have a good track record together. I will apply my knowledge and experience to help support the patient treatment goals you’re looking for with approved education and resources. These resources are designed to help you make informed prescribing decisions for your patients and support your priorities.” </welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="30">
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="10"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D060_B010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[3]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>C</b>. “Dr. Gomez, we have worked together for some time now, and I want you to know that I’d be happy to come in and do an in-service for your nursing staff at any time.” </welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="5">
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D060_C010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
		
		<choice>
			<id><![CDATA[4]]></id>
			<isCorrect><![CDATA[NO]]></isCorrect>
			<choiceText><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><b>D</b>. “OAPI can help support your patient treatment goals.  I will be sure to make you and the other Maycomb cardiologists aware of any upcoming speaker programs.”  </welcomeText>]]></choiceText>
			<KPIs totalScore="5">
				<KPI marks="5"><![CDATA[Customer Results Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Sales Progress Score]]></KPI>
				<KPI marks="0"><![CDATA[Trusted Advisor Relationship Score]]></KPI>
			</KPIs>
			<branchTo><![CDATA[OTS_SA_R3_D060_A010]]></branchTo>
		</choice>
	</choices>
	<summary><![CDATA[<welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">An effective personal value message should not focus on just the personal relationship you have with Dr. Gomez (Choice B), or just on the value OAPI can provide (Choices C and D). By addressing just the personal relationship, you miss an opportunity to reinforce the value of OAPI. At the same time, people buy from people, so it’s important to emphasize how you will partner with Dr. Gomez to help the department succeed. The best value message is one that ties back to the value map and includes both the value OAPI has to offer and how you personally will specifically work with the department to achieve their priorities (Choice A).</welcomeText>]]></summary>
</pageContent>